Wife of former President of the United States of America, Hilary Clinton has dent a strong message to President Muhammadu Buhari of Nigeria to stop killing peaceful protesters in the country. The former presidential aspirant of the Democratic Party was responding to the military onslaught of unarmed #EndSARS peaceful protesters at Lekki toll gate, Lagos on Tuesday night.
At the time of this report 78 persons had been counted dead in the military shooting.
